long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transform your WhatsApp contact extraction experience with the Contacts Extractor for wa browser extension is a sophisticated tool that simplifies the process of extracting and handling your WA contacts.

Contacts Extractor for wa is a highly efficient browser extension that is designed to extract your WA contacts and group contacts effortlessly. This user-friendly tool offers the added convenience of exporting your contacts in CSV, JSON, or Excel (XLSX) formats, making it an excellent choice for downloading WhatsApp contacts.

WhatsApp Contacts Extractor is specifically designed to make the extraction and export of your WA contacts and group contacts a cinch. Simply choose the contacts or groups you want to export, and with a click of the button "Export Contacts", your contacts list is ready for download.

Once you've extracted your desired contacts, the extension allows you to download your contact list in several formats including CSV, JSON, and XLSX(Excel) format. This versatility enables you to use your lists in a variety of applications or for various purposes, depending entirely on your needs. 

The exported contacts list provides you with essential details about each contact including Display Name, Public Name, Formatted Name, Phone, Formatted Phone, Country Code, Country Name, whether the contact belongs to you or it is blocked or a business contact, Labels, Last Message, Last Message Date, Last Message Status, Last Message From Me, and when it was scraped. This wealth of information makes the extension an invaluable tool for managing your contacts effectively.

How to Use Contacts Extractor for wa.
1. Launch https://web.whatsapp.com/ You’ll find the export button above the chat window on the left. Click this button to open a dialog box where you can select the contacts or groups you want to export.
2. Click "Export Contacts" to begin the extraction of your WhatsApp contacts list. 
3. Click the "Download Items" button to save your contacts as a local file, available in your chosen format.

Data Privacy
Your data stays on your device and is not stored or transmitted to our servers. We prioritize keeping your information secure and confidential.

Disclaimer
This extension is an independently developed product by ExtensionsBox and has no association with WhatsApp LLC.
